2. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) - The paper proposes a new method of improving the performance of molecular communication by defining a counting region on the spherical receiver's surface. 4. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper proposes a new method of improving the performance of molecular communication by defining a counting region on the spherical receiver's surface. This involves control and optimization, which are key areas of research in systems and control.
